CANGEN v. CRAMER et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. June 23, 1917.) No. 255. Appeal from District Court of tile United States for the Eastern District of New York. William E. Warland, of New York City, for appellant. James R. Hodder, of Boston, Mass., for appellees.

Before COXE, WARD, and HOUGH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
